00:00:18.580 --> 00:00:20.670
Find a house in
three easy steps.

00:00:20.670 --> 00:00:23.340
Look on our website,
see the property

00:00:23.340 --> 00:00:26.130
that you're interested
in, and then we attach you

00:00:26.130 --> 00:00:30.880
to one of our offline
agents, who would then

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:33.510
help you find-- who
would then basically

00:00:33.510 --> 00:00:36.890
walk you through the process
of getting the house.

00:00:36.890 --> 00:00:40.960
What we did was
to basically have

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:45.380
absolutely no human
interaction with users.

00:00:45.380 --> 00:00:49.180
We had started a classifieds
website at the time.

00:00:49.180 --> 00:00:51.710
And what we did, we
basically did not

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:54.810
interface with the
users that much.

00:00:54.810 --> 00:00:58.220
However, just from our
contact page alone,

00:00:58.220 --> 00:01:01.360
we then started getting emails.

00:01:01.360 --> 00:01:05.370
We were inundated
with emails basically

00:01:05.370 --> 00:01:10.570
