00:01:15.140 --> 00:01:18.430
What we decided to do
after that was to set up

00:01:18.430 --> 00:01:21.510
our customer service center.

00:01:21.510 --> 00:01:25.150
We put up our phone
numbers on the website,

00:01:25.150 --> 00:01:27.580
