around with our pilot team.

00:02:00.350 --> 00:02:02.940
The pilot testers
had already gone out.

00:02:02.940 --> 00:02:04.070
We had gotten feedback.

00:02:04.070 --> 00:02:06.050
We had looked at
our business model.

00:02:06.050 --> 00:02:08.630
We had spoken to
partner agencies.

00:02:08.630 --> 00:02:13.390
Everything basically-- we
made sure everything added up.

